   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Aurelii Apollonios and Ptolemaios, overseer of the chaff for Babylon. Has brought Priscus, for Karanis, one basket (sargane) of chaff, for the 19th and 18th and 11th year, on Pauni 19.</ab>
